{Footpaths and Rights of Way}
There are{13 footpaths}in our survey area.They lead mostly through fields making a pleasant walk,and cutting out roads.Most of the time the fields that are used for the{footpaths}are grass. These are some of the{footpaths.}
Lezant to Trebullett Hill. Lezant to Bottonnet. Penscombe to loop via Penscombe Cross. Mounthawke to squares out of our area. Lowely Bridge to the A388. Near Lowely Brook to Penscombe Cross. Moorview to Carvoda. Carvoda to the A388.
